00:56:18,030 --> 00:56:22,480
 Dating was the last thing she wanted. I convinced her to go on a blind date, 

800
00:56:22,480 --> 00:56:24,790
 and she ended up meeting you. 

801
00:56:24,790 --> 00:56:29,760
 - Really? 
 - I don't know what happened between you two, 

802
00:56:30,950 --> 00:56:35,880
 but I want Hong Ju to be happy. 

803
00:56:35,880 --> 00:56:39,710
 And you passed my test yesterday. 

804
00:56:39,710 --> 00:56:41,130
 I feel so supported. 

805
00:56:41,130 --> 00:56:43,090
 Did you confess to her yet? 

806
00:56:43,090 --> 00:56:47,950
 She said I was just her classmate Number Three. 

807
00:56:47,950 --> 00:56:49,520
 "Classmate Number Three"? 

808
00:56:49,520 --> 00:56:52,170
 She doesn't even have classmates Number One or Two. 

809
00:56:52,170 --> 00:56:54,110
 So what will you do? 

810
00:56:54,110 --> 00:56:56,870
 I should get the number removed first. 

811
00:57:01,280 --> 00:57:04,660
I said that when I was feeling weak

812
00:57:04,660 --> 00:57:06,280
since I fell in the pit due to you.

813
00:57:06,280 --> 00:57:08,380
That has...

814
00:57:08,380 --> 00:57:10,030
no legal power.

815
00:57:10,030 --> 00:57:13,560
I don't think we were feeling that weak.

816
00:57:13,560 --> 00:57:14,840
We were.

817
00:57:14,840 --> 00:57:18,280
We fell into the pit stuck all night. How were we not weak?

818
00:57:18,280 --> 00:57:20,080
I wasn't.

819
00:57:20,080 --> 00:57:21,410
I was, okay?

820
00:57:21,410 --> 00:57:24,530
 People say random things before they die. 

821
00:57:24,530 --> 00:57:26,210
And let's make this clear.

822
00:57:26,210 --> 00:57:28,080
I said, "If I become a director."

823
00:57:28,080 --> 00:57:31,640
I'm not a director. I'm just an employee at a production company.

824
00:57:31,640 --> 00:57:34,820
So that promise doesn't count. It doesn't.

825
00:57:36,820 --> 00:57:38,650
Are you laughing?

826
00:57:39,310 --> 00:57:43,310
I didn't think you'd argue so seriously about it.

827
00:57:43,310 --> 00:57:45,970
Lee Hong Ju, you really...

828
00:57:45,970 --> 00:57:47,510
What?

829
00:57:50,980 --> 00:57:53,320
Gosh, Kang Hu Yeong.

830
00:57:53,320 --> 00:57:55,690
I answered seriously because it was you.

831
00:57:55,690 --> 00:57:58,510
I thought you were trying to manage my income.

832
00:57:58,510 --> 00:58:02,080
You're also inhuman. Kang Hu Yeong is like a smart preschooler.

833
00:58:02,080 --> 00:58:05,000
Because you'd be more than capable of that.

834
00:58:05,000 --> 00:58:07,700
Does your salary for the last ten years total 1 billion won (720,000 USD)?

835
00:58:07,700 --> 00:58:10,700
I don't deal with anything below 1 billion won.

836
00:58:10,700 --> 00:58:14,800
- Five percent of 10 billion is only ₩500 million ($368,000). 
 - Oh, I see.

837
00:58:14,800 --> 00:58:17,650
You're so impressive.

838
00:58:27,900 --> 00:58:29,650
How is work? Is it fun?

839
00:58:29,650 --> 00:58:31,160
Whatever.

840
00:58:31,160 --> 00:58:32,470
How could work be fun?

841
00:58:32,470 --> 00:58:34,390
It's only fun watching animations.

842
00:58:34,390 --> 00:58:36,270
Do you know how labor-intensive it is?

843
00:58:36,270 --> 00:58:39,140
I started by collecting receipts.

844
00:58:39,140 --> 00:58:40,820
And how dare you joke about taking 5%

845
00:58:40,820 --> 00:58:43,490
of the tiny salary I worked so hard for?

846
00:58:43,490 --> 00:58:46,250
I was just happy to see you again.

847
00:58:46,250 --> 00:58:50,350
I didn't know you were actually making animations.

848
00:58:50,350 --> 00:58:53,060
I told you. I'm just in a planning team.

849
00:58:53,060 --> 00:58:56,460
I might not be a director,

850
00:58:56,460 --> 00:58:59,780
but I'll debut as a producer this time.

851
00:58:59,780 --> 00:59:02,480
Wow, how impressive.

852
00:59:03,580 --> 00:59:07,130
You always surpass my expectations.

853
00:59:07,130 --> 00:59:09,770
Well, I suppose I tend to do that.

854
00:59:11,980 --> 00:59:15,830
Do you want to watch our work if you have time?

855
00:59:15,830 --> 00:59:18,360
My name is in the ending credits too.

856
00:59:18,360 --> 00:59:20,820
Let's watch one now.

857
00:59:20,820 --> 00:59:22,930
Let me finish this first.

858
00:59:26,090 --> 00:59:27,880
Enjoy it.

859
00:59:31,880 --> 00:59:33,660
Hello.

860
00:59:46,350 --> 00:59:48,120
Excuse me,

861
00:59:48,120 --> 00:59:50,020
where is Producer Lee Hong Ju?

862
00:59:50,020 --> 00:59:52,110
"Producer Lee"?

863
01:00:00,720 --> 01:00:01,890
I'm tired.

864
01:00:01,890 --> 01:00:03,820
I'll go get my laptop.

865
01:00:03,820 --> 01:00:05,180
Do you want me to carry you again?

866
01:00:05,180 --> 01:00:07,520
No, okay?

867
01:00:07,520 --> 01:00:09,390
It's easier not to use the crutches.

868
01:00:09,390 --> 01:00:11,840
I'll jump using one foot.

869
01:00:15,690 --> 01:00:17,500
Stay away.

870
01:00:23,400 --> 01:00:25,400
Lee Hong Ju.

871
01:00:40,290 --> 01:00:43,290
What brings you here, Mr. Bang?

872
01:00:45,070 --> 01:00:48,620
I heard the meeting got postponed due to an accident.

873
01:00:49,570 --> 01:00:51,700
But it doesn't seem that way.

874
01:00:54,370 --> 01:00:56,480
I'm sorry the schedule was changed due to me, but—

875
01:00:56,480 --> 01:00:59,310
Is this how much you care about your work?

876
01:01:00,200 --> 01:01:03,100
If you neglect things like this,

877
01:01:03,100 --> 01:01:08,100
I'll have to reconsider working with you.

878
01:01:09,600 --> 01:01:12,340
You—

879
01:01:24,600 --> 01:01:26,600
Fire me then.

880
01:01:28,110 --> 01:01:31,610
Lee Hong Ju, what's wrong with you?

881
01:01:31,610 --> 01:01:35,220
I'll be so upset if you don't know why I do this.

882
01:01:38,550 --> 01:01:41,630
You said you wouldn't change your mind.

883
01:01:41,630 --> 01:01:44,390
You said you'd never change.

884
01:01:44,390 --> 01:01:46,780
You're the one who said it.

885
01:01:46,780 --> 01:01:48,830
Did I say that?

886
01:01:50,310 --> 01:01:52,400
I'm sorry,

887
01:01:52,400 --> 01:01:54,700
but I've changed.

888
01:01:55,840 --> 01:01:58,300
You understand why now, right?

889
01:01:58,300 --> 01:02:00,690
Then could you leave now?

890
01:02:02,500 --> 01:02:05,070
I didn't finish talking to you yet.

891
01:02:05,070 --> 01:02:07,170
If you touch me one more time,

892
01:02:07,170 --> 01:02:09,840
I'll beat you up.

893
01:03:39,470 --> 01:03:41,490
Why are you sitting here like this?

894
01:03:41,490 --> 01:03:43,360
Because my foot hurts.

895
01:03:43,360 --> 01:03:45,950
You said you'd jump up with one foot.

896
01:03:45,950 --> 01:03:49,190
Why did you act strong in your condition?

897
01:04:02,120 --> 01:04:03,780
Does it hurt a lot?

898
01:04:03,780 --> 01:04:05,930
It freaking hurts,

899
01:04:06,870 --> 01:04:09,800
and I'm embarrassed.

900
01:04:09,800 --> 01:04:13,790
I'm embarrassed that you keep finding out about my failed relationship.

901
01:04:15,360 --> 01:04:17,980
You're making me feel bad.

902
01:04:18,850 --> 01:04:20,880
I'm happy

903
01:04:20,880 --> 01:04:23,350
that your relationship failed.

904
01:04:33,390 --> 01:04:37,620
This reminds me of when we fell into the pit.

905
01:04:39,980 --> 01:04:43,500
Stop reminding me of the past I want to forget.

906
01:04:49,210 --> 01:04:50,970
Lee Hong Ju.

907
01:04:53,670 --> 01:04:55,760
Recover soon,

908
01:04:55,760 --> 01:04:59,180
your foot and your heart too.

909
01:05:30,050 --> 01:05:40,210
♫  There are so many things I want to tell you  ♫

910
01:05:40,210 --> 01:05:45,000
    
 ♫  Standing in front of you again  ♫

911
01:05:45,000 --> 01:05:52,210
♫  For a long time I'm unable to say a word  ♫

912
01:05:52,210 --> 01:05:56,480
♫  I love you so much  ♫

913
01:05:56,480 --> 01:05:59,730
♫  Why is it so hard to say this?  ♫

914
01:05:59,730 --> 01:06:02,660
 Memories are unreliable. 

915
01:06:02,660 --> 01:06:07,890
 Because only one person remembers some memories. 

916
01:06:07,890 --> 01:06:17,050
♫  I always want to be by your side  ♫

917
