918
01:06:59,650 --> 01:07:01,590
 Kang Hu Yeong. 

919
01:07:06,160 --> 01:07:08,550
 What's going on with me? 

920
01:07:09,930 --> 01:07:15,060
 My heart started racing just now. 

921
01:07:30,240 --> 01:07:32,980
♫  I feel so strange these days  ♫

922
01:07:32,980 --> 01:07:37,210
♫  It's really not like me. All day I think of you  ♫

923
01:07:37,210 --> 01:07:41,210
 I must be the only one who was shocked. 

924
01:07:41,210 --> 01:07:43,840
♫  I can't stop worrying about you  ♫

925
01:07:43,840 --> 01:07:46,290
 Memories are unreliable. 

926
01:07:46,290 --> 01:07:49,920
♫  My heart is pounding  ♫

927
01:07:49,920 --> 01:07:51,940
♫  It's you  ♫

928
01:07:51,940 --> 01:07:55,670
♫  The destiny I've been waiting for  ♫

929
01:07:55,670 --> 01:08:00,600
♫  Why has it arrived only now?  ♫

930
01:08:00,600 --> 01:08:03,650
♫  I see only you. I hear only you  ♫

931
01:08:03,650 --> 01:08:06,630
♫  It has to be you  ♫

932
01:08:06,630 --> 01:08:13,480
♫  No matter what, I don't want to lose you  ♫

933
01:08:15,720 --> 01:08:21,430
♫  I never believed in destiny  ♫

934
01:08:22,820 --> 01:08:25,700
 Rethink it carefully starting now. 

935
01:08:25,700 --> 01:08:28,850
 Are we really just friends? 

936
01:08:28,850 --> 01:08:31,300
 - I said things are awkward between us. 
 - Hey, Hu Yeong! 

937
01:08:31,300 --> 01:08:33,200
 I'm having more fun now. 

938
01:08:33,200 --> 01:08:36,130
 You keep showing interest in me. 

939
01:08:36,970 --> 01:08:41,070
 Just forget about Kang Hu Yeong and have fun. 

940
01:08:41,890 --> 01:08:44,790
 You tried to kiss me just now, right? 

941
01:08:44,790 --> 01:08:47,780
 I'm here to pick up Hu Yeong. 

942
01:08:47,780 --> 01:08:49,470
 Are you going somewhere? 

943
01:08:49,470 --> 01:08:51,610
 You really want me to leave? 

944
01:08:51,610 --> 01:08:54,650
♫  It has to be you  ♫

